00:18:56.801 --> 00:18:58.561
When I took up arms.

00:18:58.721 --> 00:19:02.761
I went from being a teacher
to a man of arms.

00:19:02.921 --> 00:19:04.361
I had no choice.

00:19:04.521 --> 00:19:08.241
