Would you forgive me
if I kill your father or brother?

00:23:41.401 --> 00:23:43.761
If no law stands in my way?

00:23:44.481 --> 00:23:46.441
If your rights are scorned?

00:23:46.601 --> 00:23:48.121
Would you forgive me

